      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/plastic-treaty-talks-behind-schedule-amid-impasse-over-production-limits-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于世界对其第一个塑料条约应有多大的雄心仍存在分歧，各国正在考虑在 12 月达成预期协议之前召开一系列小型会议。]]></description>
