    <item>
      <title>中国比亚迪第一季度盈利疲弱，价格战显现影响</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-effects-price-war-with-weaker-profit-growth-2024-04-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国电动汽车 (EV) 制造商比亚迪周一公布了自 2022 年以来最弱的季度利润增长，同时，由于电动汽车需求放缓和全球最大汽车市场激烈的价格战，其收入增长放缓至近四年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-effects-price-war-with-weaker-profit-growth-2024-04-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 11:12:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
